title: Harriet Tubman Underground Railroad National Historical Park: Management
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Management             Management       Harriet Tubman Underground Railroad National Monument was created by Presidential Proclamation on March 25, 2013. It is one of the newest additions to the national park system. Harriet Tubman Underground Railroad National Monument is one of about 400 units in the National Park System.
